{{version025}}
{{flavour|Brings the air into unnatural stillness across a huge area, preventing anything short of a tornado from breaking the calm. The effect takes concentration to maintain, and only lasts a short time; if the caster is killed, clouds begin to form again as normal.}}

'''Still Winds''' is a monster-only spell which prevents the creation of [[cloud]]s, including through spells ([[Conjure Flame]], [[Poisonous Vapours]], [[Mephitic Cloud]], [[Freezing Cloud]], [[Corpse Rot]], etc.), items ([[scroll of fog]], [[wand of clouds]]), and environmental effects (such as the perpetual salt storms in the [[Desolation of Salt]]). It also removes all existing clouds from the whole floor. The player gains the {{Brown|-Clouds}} [[status effect|status]] for the duration.

Still Winds has no effect on [[Tornado]].

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
The spell was added in [[0.19]].

